        "This image depicts a modern, minimalist living room bathed in warm, natural light. The room is characterized by its clean lines, neutral color palette, and sophisticated design.\n\n**Key Features:**\n\n- **The TV:** A large, sleek, wall-mounted television is the focal point, displaying a vibrant, high-resolution image of a forest in autumn with golden trees. It sits on a low, minimalist wooden media console that also holds a small potted plant and a stack of books.\n\n- **Seating:** A contemporary, beige or light taupe-colored modular sofa or lounge chair is positioned on a textured, dark brown area rug. The chair has a soft, rounded design and is accented with a single, plush pillow.\n\n- **Coffee Table:** A simple, round, dark wood coffee table with a low profile sits in the center of the rug, holding a decorative, spherical wireframe object.\n\n- **Windows and View:** A large, floor-to-ceiling window dominates one wall, offering a stunning view of an expansive, sunlit field with trees in autumn colors. The window is dressed with sheer, white vertical blinds that allow soft, diffused light to enter the room.\n\n- **Lighting:** The room is illuminated by recessed LED strip lighting along the ceiling's edge, creating a warm, ambient glow. The natural light from the window enhances the room's airy and open feel.\n\n- **Materials and Finish:** The floor is made of polished, dark wood, and the walls are finished in a light, neutral tone. The furniture and cabinetry feature a natural wood finish, contributing to the room's warm, organic aesthetic.\n\nOverall, the space conveys a sense of calm, luxury, and modern comfort, with a strong emphasis on natural materials and an uncluttered, serene atmosphere."
      ],
      "shape": 4
    },
